name: Shiv Sai thali house palolem beach Road Palolem Beach canacona goa.

reviews.review_text:
They serve the best fish and veg thalis.
The quantity of the curries are perfect. Plus the amount of rice is also good and coming to taste. It's just yumm.. pricing is also reasonable.

Their prawns masala fry (goan style) is also yumm. One must try it for sure. You will not find as such at least in palolem for sure.

You can even try fish steak and chicken sizzlers/butter garlic prawns . It's worth the price and tasty.

But you must not miss their Banana Fritters with ice cream. It's just perfect.

The owners are friendly!!! It has a good goan vibe!!
This hotel is very near to Palolem beach (Center of south Goa). The service is very good along with a staff. The food is very delicious. We went after 9.00 PM so eperienced very chill ambience.

The place is famous for its thalis and rightly so! The service is quick and the staff always smiles. We tried a lot of items from the menu and my personal favorite would be dal tadka and veg jalfrezi. You can skip fried rice though. Special appreciation for their 'never say no' attitude.

description:
**Discovering Shiv Sai Thali House: A Culinary Gem on Palolem Beach**

Nestled along the vibrant Palolem Beach Road in Canacona, Goa, **Shiv Sai Thali House** boasts an impressive 4.2-star rating garnered from over **810 reviews.** Renowned for its **fish thalis**, Goan cuisine, and lively seafood offerings, this restaurant has quickly become a favorite for those seeking delightful meals without straining their budgets.

**Ambiance & Design**

Visually inviting, Shiv Sai Thali House presents a laid-back atmosphere infused with a distinct Goan vibe. A blend of warm lighting and rustic decor creates an inviting space that mirrors the region’s coastal charm. Images from delighted diners showcase cheerful interiors, hinting at a casual yet comfortable setting perfect for unwinding after a day at the beach. With relaxing music and a chill ambience, particularly during their later hours, the restaurant makes for an ideal dining destination.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The menu at Shiv Sai Thali House is a testament to the richness of Goan cuisine, with their **thalis** earning particular acclaim. Diners rave about the perfect quantity of curries and rice, consistently bringing a smile to their faces. Highlights include the **prawns masala fry** prepared in traditional Goan style, delicious **fish steaks**, and satisfying **chicken sizzlers**. Vegetarians will find solace in dishes like **dal tadka** and **veg jalfrezi**, both praised for their taste and quality. For dessert, **banana fritters topped with ice cream** are not to be missed—a sublime ending to an otherwise hearty meal.

The restaurant also caters well to various dietary preferences, ensuring that there is something for everyone.

**Customer Experience & Service**

Customer reviews overwhelmingly commend the prompt and friendly service at Shiv Sai Thali House. Guests appreciate the staff’s cheerful demeanor and their **'never say no' attitude**, which enhances the overall dining experience. The restaurant welcomes walk-ins and maintains an efficient system to handle busy evenings, ensuring patrons do not wait long to enjoy their meals.

**Popularity & Reviews**

The buzz surrounding Shiv Sai Thali House is palpable, as locals and visitors alike take to social media to share their positive experiences. With notable dishes consistently highlighted, it’s clear why word-of-mouth has contributed so significantly to its popularity. While there are no specific critic ratings mentioned, the restaurant has undoubtedly earned its place in the hearts of its patrons.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

Customer photos reveal not only the enticing presentation of meals, from vibrant thalis to appetizing seafood dishes, but also showcase the inviting ambiance of the space. The warm colors and carefully arranged dishes invite diners to indulge, supporting the restaurant's reputation for a satisfying dining experience.

In summary, **Shiv Sai Thali House** stands out as a remarkable culinary destination on Palolem Beach. With its flavorful dishes, welcoming service, and authentic Goan atmosphere, it promises an unforgettable dining experience worthy of exploration by anyone visiting the area.
